937
01:16:41,629 --> 01:16:42,630
Aku beruntung.

938
01:16:42,730 --> 01:16:44,332
Angkat tangan.
Pandangan lurus.

939
01:16:45,100 --> 01:16:46,301
Angkat tangan!

940
01:16:49,938 --> 01:16:52,340
